-- Berlusconi Says Naples Area to Be Clear of Trash Pileup Within Three Days
-- B y   J e f f r e y   D o n o v a n
-- 2010-10-28T11:57:07Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-28/berlusconi-says-naples-area-to-be-clear-of-trash-pileup-within-three-days.html
Italian Prime Minister Silvio
Berlusconi said that a pileup of garbage in the Naples area that
has led to violent protests will be cleared up in three days.  He made his comments at a news conference in the town of
Acerra near the southern port city.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jeffrey Donovan at 
 jdonovan26@bloomberg.net  